{"tid":1986819,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：預料第四季支那客可訪港 倡開拓親近大自然旅遊","createTime":"2020-04-24T05:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T10:45:08.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"837db18ed0ec64a3099f18f631a9e0b740307b92","tid":1986819,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"旅發局料旅遊業將現新常態 港應審視定位<br />\n24.04.2020 12:56<br />\n<br />\n旅發局主席彭耀佳預料旅遊業將出現新常態，旅遊習慣會在疫情後有所改變，旅客首要考慮公共衛生安全，傾向挑選低健康風險的旅遊目的地，香港應重新審視旅遊定位。旅發局向業界舉行網上簡報會，分析疫情過後，短途市場及新市場會先以本土旅遊為主，外遊亦會緊接展開，但受經濟及假期等因素限制，將傾向選擇短途旅程，又預料經過長期居家抗疫之後，旅客更著重健康及親近大自然，健康主題概念的行程將會是新趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局預料疫情過後，亞裔客群將是首批訪港的旅客。至於長途客市場，需要較長時間恢復，旅客最快要到第4季起才開始外遊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283045&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1283045%26csid%3D261_341&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hcljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=d374dd2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283045&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"f24da6c933f93f86712d7a992e5235ccaf387d4d","tid":1986819,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c5aa67ac8427e2e725246bc13715dc0f84a40b","tid":1986819,"uid":19842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"香港d山變成堆填區指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近排d山沿路都係口罩紙巾垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f0afb0c63a9d24e2afced61fbe92b0165be2b8","tid":1986819,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"而家啲山已經咁多垃圾<br 